  EffectDiscription_ENG: "\uFF1CScapegoat\uFF1E (When this Digimon would be deleted
    other than by your effects, by deleting 1 of your other Digimon, prevent that
    deletion)\n[On Play] [When Digivolving] Trash 1 card in your opponent's hand
    without looking.\n[All Turns] [Once Per Turn] When a card is trashed from your
    opponent's hand, you may play 1 purple card with a play cost 10 or less from
    your trash without paying the cost. For each card in your opponent's hand, reduce
    this effect's play cost maximum by 1."
